- put the macbook makefiles in your lammps directory's src/MAKE/MINE path and run "make clean-liammac(_mpi); make liammac(_mpi) -j4" to compile the serial (mpi) version using four cores.
- change neighbour.cpp around line 1895 (or search "skin ="); just comment out (using //) the if that throws an error when skin is negative and you should be good to go!

git clone https://github.com/lammps/lammps.git


